# Validation Index

## Validation philosophy

Codex cannot claim success without evidence. Opus cannot accept without checking evidence.

## Default validation ladder

- L0: build/typecheck/lint/compile
- L1: targeted unit tests
- L2: integration tests
- L3: system/e2e/smoke tests
- L4: domain/platform-specific validation
- L5: human approval gate

